quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  81,1,"When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]"
  81,2,"And when the stars fall, dispersing,"
  81,3,"And when the mountains are removed"
  81,4,"And when full-term she-camels<sup foot_note=197714>1</sup> are neglected",footnotes:197714:1
  81,5,"And when the wild beasts are gathered"
  81,6,"And when the seas are filled with flame<sup foot_note=197715>1</sup>",footnotes:197715:1
  81,7,"And when the souls are paired<sup foot_note=197716>1</sup>",footnotes:197716:1
  81,8,"And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked"
  81,9,"For what sin she was killed"
  81,10,"And when the pages<sup foot_note=197717>1</sup> are spread [i.e., made public]",footnotes:197717:1